v.
Charles P. MCCOY, a/k/a Paris McCoy, Defendant-Petitioner. C-570 September Term 2017
079931 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 2, 2018 **139To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005467-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;
